text: Zandra Nowell (born 10 September 1936) is a British alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:British female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Great Britain Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Northwich
